{{multiple issues| {{notability|event|date=June 2015}} {{primary sources|date=June 2015}} {{original research|date=June 2015}} }} {{Infobox holiday |holiday_name = Random Acts of Kindness Day |type = |image = |imagesize = |caption = |official_name = |nickname = |observedby = |litcolor = |longtype = |significance = |begins = |ends = |date = |scheduling = 1 September |duration = 1 day |frequency = annual |celebrations = |observances = |relatedto = }} '''Random Acts of Kindness Day''' is a day to celebrate and encourage [[random acts of kindness]]. "It's just a day to celebrate kindness and the whole [[pay it forward]] mentality", said Tracy Van Kalsbeek, executive director of the Stratford Perth Community Foundation, in 2016, where the day is celebrated on November 4.<ref>{{cite web|author=Beitz, Mike |publisher=The Beacon Herald|url=http://www.stratfordbeaconherald.com/2016/10/21/stratford-and-area-set-to-celebrate-random-acts-of-kindness-day |title=Stratford and area set to celebrate Random Acts of Kindness Day |accessdate=October 24, 2016}}</ref> It is celebrated on September 1 in New Zealand and on February 17 in the US.<ref>{{cite web|author=Cain, Brenda Cain |publisher=cleveland.com|url=http://www.cleveland.com/best/2016/02/feb_17_is_random_acts_of_kindn.html |title=Today is Random Acts of Kindness Day; nominate someone for February Person of the Month |accessdate=October 24, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|publisher=Random Acts of Kindness Foundation|url=https://www.randomactsofkindness.org/ |title=Random Acts of Kindness Day |accessdate=October 24, 2016}}</ref><ref>http://www.azcentral.com/story/inside-12/2015/02/16/12-news-12-random-acts-of-kindness/23523321/</ref>
==Background==
The Random Acts of Kindness Foundation (RAK) was founded in 1995 in the US. It is a nonprofit headquartered in Denver, Colorado.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Random Acts of Kindness Foundation|url=https://www.randomactsofkindness.org/faq |title=Random Acts of Kindness FAQs |accessdate=October 24, 2016}}</ref>
Random Acts of Kindness (RAK) day began in 2004 in New Zealand.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Random Acts of Kindness Day (New Zealand) |url=http://rak.co.nz/rak-ideas/ |title=Fun RAK Ideas |accessdate=October 24, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rak.co.nz/RAKInformation/News/tabid/56/ctl/ArticleView/mid/399/articleId/3/Be-Kind-to-others--its-that-sort-of-day.aspx |title=Be Kind to others ... it's that sort of day |publisher=[[Hawkes Bay Today]] |date=September 1, 2005 |accessdate=January 4, 2013 |author=Moroney, Roger |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100525230205/http://www.rak.co.nz/RAKInformation/News/tabid/56/ctl/ArticleView/mid/399/articleId/3/Be-Kind-to-others--its-that-sort-of-day.aspx |archivedate=May 25, 2010 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rak.co.nz/RAKInformation/RAKTeam/tabid/54/Default.aspx |title=R.A.K. Team, Josh de Jong |publisher=Random Acts of Kindness Day NZ |accessdate=January 4, 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120414101904/http://www.rak.co.nz/RAKInformation/RAKTeam/tabid/54/Default.aspx |archivedate=April 14, 2012 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|publisher=TVNZ |url=https://www.tvnz.co.nz/one-news/new-zealand/spring-starts-with-random-acts-of-kindness-6068419 |title=Today is random acts of kindness day |accessdate=October 24, 2016}}</ref> {{better source needed|date=June 2015}}
==Suggested activities== Ideas include: * Pay for the person behind you in the drive-thru * Let someone go ahead of you in line * Buy extra at the grocery store and donate it to a food pantry * Buy flowers for someone (postal worker, grocery store clerk, bus driver, etc.) * Help someone change a flat tire * Post anonymous sticky notes with validating or uplifting messages around for people to find * Compliment a work colleague on their work * Send an encouraging text to someone * Take muffins to work * Let a car into the traffic ahead of you * Wash someone else's car * Take a gift to new neighbors and introduce yourself * Pay the bus fare for the passenger behind you<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Random Acts of Kindness Day (New Zealand) |url=http://rak.co.nz/rak-ideas/ |title=Fun RAK Ideas |accessdate=October 24, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Cain, Brenda Cain |publisher=cleveland.com|url=http://www.cleveland.com/best/2016/02/feb_17_is_random_acts_of_kindn.html |title=Today is Random Acts of Kindness Day; nominate someone for February Person of the Month |accessdate=October 24, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|publisher=Random Acts of Kindness Foundation|url=https://www.randomactsofkindness.org/kindness-ideas |title=Random Acts of Kindness Day Ideas |accessdate=October 24, 2016}}</ref>
